---

<section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="section-inner reveal">
        <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>

        <p class="about-text">
            We're a family duo &mdash; cousins who share a love for beautiful, meaningful jewelry.
            Linked by Love was born from the idea that the best accessories are the ones you never take off.
            We bring the magic of permanent jewelry to farmers markets and events across Virginia and Maryland,
            creating custom pieces that celebrate your connections, milestones, and everyday sparkle.
        </p>

        <div class="about-features">
            <div class="about-feature">
                <span class="about-feature-icon">&#10022;</span>
                <h3>Handcrafted</h3>
                <p>Every piece is custom-fitted and welded just for you, right before your eyes</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-feature">
                <span class="about-feature-icon">&#8734;</span>
                <h3>Permanent</h3>
                <p>No clasps to fiddle with &mdash; your jewelry stays on through every moment of life</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-feature">
                <span class="about-feature-icon">&#9825;</span>
                <h3>Meaningful</h3>
                <p>Perfect for best friends, couples, mother &amp; daughter, or a treat just for you</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about {
        background: white;
    }

    .about-text {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto 50px;
        color: var(--text-light);
        line-height: 2;
    }

    .about-features {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 40px;
        margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .about-feature {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .about-feature-icon {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        display: block;
        color: var(--gold);
    }

    .about-feature h3 {
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--rose);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .about-feature p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-light);
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .about-features {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
        }
    }
</style>
